Ideograms are currently input using the letter 'i' followed by the last two hex digits
of the ideograms Unicode character code. For example, the ideogram for man would be input
using "i80" in the input box since the character code for this ideogram is 00010080.

Font used: The Aegean font at http://users.teilar.gr/~g1951d/
Related Unicode documents:
Linear B Syllabary: http://unicode.org/charts/PDF/U10000.pdf
Linear B Ideograms: http://unicode.org/charts/PDF/U10080.pdf
Aegean Numbers: http://unicode.org/charts/PDF/U10100.pdf